### Get all task statuses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/statuses

### Get task status by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/statuses/1

### Create a new task status
POST http://localhost:8080/api/statuses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status_name": "Blocked"
}

